snippet.title: Neighbor - 2nd Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Sometimes, in life, there are places where the rules of reality just don't apply. Sometimes it's the one place where you ought to feel safe. Like your house.

Get ready to visit Châtelet Romane and meet your Neighbor! Featuring amazing voice talent like Rie Kawamura (Shounen Ashibe: Go! Go! Goma-chan), this thrilling horror visual novel will begin its production in Spring 2018. 

Check out our website and subscribe to our newsletter: https://www.otusunland.com/
